@startuml
!theme plain
title 17. Research Metadata Workflow
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "arXiv API/S3/bulk data" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Local RAG archive" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Metadata index" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Markdown/LaTeX/BibTeX" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Publication package" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : metadata
N2 --> N3 : PDF/source tar
N3 --> N4 : SQLite/JSONL
N4 --> N5 : citations

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
